•Presentation:
	•Analysing computer networks threats and prevention
	•In your summative group, create a presentation demonstrating an awareness of the security threats to networks connected to the internet and how these should be managed (prevented).

•Presentation will be produced using Pechakucha:
	•20 slides (or pictures), each shown for 20s. 
	•You can record audio for each slide individually, using your web browser.
	•The link of your created presentation should be sent to your module tutor.
